name: Chingri Pulao
about: Fresh Chingri infused in nuts and malai with rice to give you the real feels of simplicity!

name: Ilish Pulao
about: Ilish Pulao, made with Ilish fish (Hilsa), is a delicious and extremely fragrant Bangali rice dish, popular all over Bengal .
